The paper deals with object detection, which is a core topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves designing a proposal distribution and updating it based on rejection, acceptance, and ambiguity windows, which involves learning and optimization (cs.LG, cs.AI). The paper also presents experimental results on human and face detection, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM) and computer security (cs.CR) applications.
